The Ames spy case apparently used electronic eavesdropping to get the
goods on him.  The affidavit for arrest said that the FBI had a monitor
in the Ames' computer.  The FBI and US atty wouldn't confirm or deny.
The FBI probably uses a chip made by the NSA which includes FFT - Fast
Fourier Transform - to improve reception quality.
